translations: n.上颌骨，上颌；（节肢动物）下颚（maxilla 的复数）

sentences.sentence: Conclusion the palatal vault, cusp inclination and the position of artificial teeth have apparent influence upon the stress concentration on the alveoli dentales maxillae.

sentences.sentence: The ventral nerve cord of the crab in the embryo included 1 pair mandibular neuromere, 2 pairs neuromeres of maxillae, 2 pairs neuromeres of maxillipede and abdomen nerve cord.
sentences.translation: 三疣梭子蟹胚胎期腹神经链由1对大颚、2对小颚和2对颚足所对应的神经节以及腹部神经链组成。
